<!-- ============================================================
     SCROLL-EXPAND MEDIA  (the "fills-the-viewport as you scroll" block)

     Write the tag inline in markdown anywhere in the body. Required:
       type  — "image" | "video" | "component"
       src   — URL or /public path (image/video)
       component — key in HERO_COMPONENTS (when type="component")

     Optional:
       poster    — video poster frame
       alt       — accessible label
       contained — "true" to render a static card instead of scroll-expand

     Examples (uncomment to use):
============================================================ -->

